---
import Section from '../Section.astro';

import Technologies from '../sections/Technologies.astro';
import Languages from '../sections/Languages.astro';
---

<Section title="About me">
  <div class="about-container">
    <div class="about-technologies">
      <Technologies />
      <Languages />
    </div>
    <div class="about-text">
      <p>
        I'm a UX/UI Designer and Fullstack Developer who proudly holds both
        Argentinian and Italian citizenship. I'm also an "Advocate" according to
        the 16 Personalities test, which means I care deeply about the world
        (and probably overanalyze my coffee orders).
      </p>
      <p>
        I blend analytical thinking with creativity to craft digital products
        that are as functional and intuitive as possible. My focus is on
        delivering high-quality, user-centered solutions while enjoying every
        step of the process.
      </p>
      <p class="little-text">
        When I'm not designing or coding, you’ll likely find me strumming
        guitar, reading, or enjoying a great coffee, always exploring new ideas.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Section>

<style>
  .about-container {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  p {
    font-size: 1.64rem;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: var(--color-texto);
  }

  .about-technologies {
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .little-text {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 200;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-container {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 4rem;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
  }
</style>
